          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1664189721731-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1664189721731-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>baharat meatballs</strong> over the <strong>mash </strong>with the <strong>za'atar green beans</strong> to the side</p><p>Drizzle any <strong>remaining za'atar butter</strong> from the beans over the mash</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
